{"title":"原码补码反码","uid":"e00197cb67c593c22541d2c0932f4c40","slug":"原码反码补码","date":"2025-11-13T07:39:39.000Z","updated":"2025-11-13T09:04:21.960Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/原码反码补码.json","keywords":"Catice, 猫冰","cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"0-前置知识\"><a href=\"#0-前置知识\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"0.前置知识\"></a>0.前置知识</h2><p>原码反码和补码是为了解决计算机计算减法的问题，将减法当作加法计算</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-原码反码补码\"><a href=\"#1-原码反码补码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.原码反码补码\"></a>1.原码反码补码</h2><p><strong>原码</strong><br>计算机以1字节为单位<br>对于一个整数，如果表示它需要的位数少于存储它的类型的位数，则会在其余的位上补0<br>但它们的最高位有区别，用于表示是正数还是负数</p>\n<ul>\n<li>最高位0，表示正数<ul>\n<li>如char类型存储的14的原码：<code>00001110</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>最高位1，表示负数<ul>\n<li>如char类型-21原码：<code>10010101</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>反码</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>对于正数，它的反码是它本身</li>\n<li>对于负数，它的反码是除符号位以外的位数取反<ul>\n<li>如-21的反码<code>11101010</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>补码</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>对于正数，它的补码是本身</li>\n<li>对于负数，补码是反码加1<ul>\n<li>如-21的补码<code>11101011</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-计算机计算加法原理\"><a href=\"#2-计算机计算加法原理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.计算机计算加法原理\"></a>2.计算机计算加法原理</h2><p>计算机中，所有的数都是以其<strong>补码形式</strong>存储的，使用补码计算有以下优势</p>\n<ul>\n<li>减法与加法可用同一逻辑处理</li>\n<li>符号位无需特殊逻辑判断</li>\n<li>唯一的零表示</li>\n<li>边界问题也能处理(如-1 + 1 &#x3D; 0)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><del>说实话，我知道补码的原理，但实在无法理解，为什么会有这些优势</del><br><del>这个设计真的太精妙了</del></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-实例\"><a href=\"#3-实例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.实例\"></a>3.实例</h2><p><strong>a + b</strong><br>a的补码 + b的补码<br>因此，对于14 + (-21) &#x3D; -7<br>就是<code>00001110</code> + <code>11101011</code> &#x3D;  <code>11111001</code><br>计算结果就是-7的补码</p>\n<p><strong>相反数</strong><br>a的相反数-a，就是将a取反再加一<br>如7的相反数-7<br><code>00000111</code> -&gt; <code>11111000</code> -&gt; <code>11111001</code></p>\n","text":"0.前置知识原码反码和补码是为了解决计算机计算减法的问题，将减法当作加法计算 1.原码反码补码原码计算机以1字节为单位对于一个整数，如果表示它需要的位数少于存储...","permalink":"/post/原码反码补码","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":611,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"tutorial","slug":"tutorial","count":7,"path":"api/categories/tutorial.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"basics","slug":"basics","count":1,"path":"api/tags/basics.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#0-%E5%89%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">0.前置知识</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E5%8E%9F%E7%A0%81%E5%8F%8D%E7%A0%81%E8%A1%A5%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.原码反码补码</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.计算机计算加法原理</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.实例</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"猫冰","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/MB-drinking.png","link":"/","description":"小猫用来存博客的地方（也会发一点有趣的东西）","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"github":"https://github.com/C0P1Fur","twitter":"https://x.com/_Caticee","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/images/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/2140016240"}}}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"python复习笔记","uid":"1aa04ca316160db27113d53ff9e456fa","slug":"python复习笔记","date":"2025-11-14T03:07:31.000Z","updated":"2025-11-14T03:07:31.417Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/python复习笔记.json","keywords":"Catice, 猫冰","cover":null,"text":"","permalink":"/post/python复习笔记","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":0,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"猫冰","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/MB-drinking.png","link":"/","description":"小猫用来存博客的地方（也会发一点有趣的东西）","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"github":"https